data.title: Arthur Sheekman
data.meta_description: Arthur Sheekman. Writer: Die Marx Brothers im Krieg. Arthur Sheekman was born on 5 February 1901 in Chicago, Illinois, USA. He was a writer and actor, known for Die Marx Brothers im Krieg (1933), Madame macht Geschichte(n) (1953) and Roman Scandals (1933). He was married to Gloria Stuart. He died on 12 January 1978 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
data.text: Arthur Sheekman was born on February 5, 1901 in Chicago, Illinois, USA. He was a writer and actor, known for Die Marx Brothers im Krieg (1933), Madame macht Geschichte(n) (1953) and Roman Scandals (1933). He was married to Gloria Stuart. He died on January 12, 1978 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
